  <h1>Burr Grinder Settings for Espresso in 2026: How to Dial In Consistent Shots</h1>
  <p class="lead">Dialing in espresso gets much easier when you run the same sequence every time. This guide gives a practical baseline, a fast adjustment loop, and troubleshooting moves you can apply without guessing. We researched and compared common home grinder workflows so you can lock in repeatable results faster.</p>

